# Header specification

## Validate header components

* Goto home
* Validate logo is displayed
* Validate search bar is displayed
* Validate cart icon is displayed
* Validate Sign In is displayed


## Validate user lands to home page when clicked on logo

* Goto home
* Click About us link
* Validate About us page title
* Click logo
* Validate home page title


## Validate search bar

* Goto home
* Validate search bar is empty
* Type "pen" in the search bar
* Validate predictive search in dropdown display
* Click on cross icon
* Validate search bar is empty
* Type "leather" in the search bar
* Hit enter
* "Leather" should show up on search result page


## Validate cart icon on header

* Goto home
* Click cart icon
* Validate "Your shopping cart"
* Click on close icon


## Validate sign in link

* Goto home
* Click on sign in link
* Validate user is on login page